{
  "video_id": "2rZ3e9_baJg",
  "title": "The Herb Garden Grown in an Undersea Pot",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 1490.0,
      "end_time": 4323.0,
      "text": "I feel we are overusing the resources of our planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 5600.0,
      "end_time": 8809.0,
      "text": "We want to expand the possibilities of agriculture"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 8810.0,
      "end_time": 10920.0,
      "text": "in an environment where it wasn't thought"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 10920.0,
      "end_time": 13300.0,
      "text": "that you could actually grow plants."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 13300.0,
      "end_time": 14820.0,
      "text": "We think that that can really change"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 14820.0,
      "end_time": 16433.0,
      "text": "the outlook for the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 16433.0,
      "end_time": 19433.0,
      "text": "(atmospheric music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 22957.0,
      "end_time": 25870.0,
      "text": "(pleasant music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 25870.0,
      "end_time": 30670.0,
      "text": "Nemo's Garden is an alternative agriculture project"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 30670.0,
      "end_time": 33210.0,
      "text": "where we are trying to find a way to grow"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 33210.0,
      "end_time": 37500.0,
      "text": "plants underwater in underwater greenhouses."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 37500.0,
      "end_time": 41310.0,
      "text": "We have grown between 50 and 60 different species:"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 41310.0,
      "end_time": 44220.0,
      "text": "basil, different kinds of salads,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 44220.0,
      "end_time": 47452.0,
      "text": "goji, soy, sprouts, medical herbs."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 48530.0,
      "end_time": 51440.0,
      "text": "Harvesting the plants is actually very simple."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 51440.0,
      "end_time": 54230.0,
      "text": "We cut it just like we would do on land,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 54230.0,
      "end_time": 58519.0,
      "text": "and then we wrap it into reusable plastic containers"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 58520.0,
      "end_time": 61330.0,
      "text": "and we just close it up and we pick it"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 61330.0,
      "end_time": 63280.0,
      "text": "up on the surface nice and comfortable."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 66800.0,
      "end_time": 68890.0,
      "text": "The main challenges of growing plants underwater are:"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 68890.0,
      "end_time": 70950.0,
      "text": "it has never been done; it's all new."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 70950.0,
      "end_time": 73730.0,
      "text": "Initially, the learning curve was very steep."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 73730.0,
      "end_time": 76220.0,
      "text": "Every operation has to be done scuba diving,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 76220.0,
      "end_time": 77920.0,
      "text": "and that is a challenge on itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 79310.0,
      "end_time": 81380.0,
      "text": "The main advantages are the"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 81380.0,
      "end_time": 83199.0,
      "text": "protection from outside elements."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 83200.0,
      "end_time": 85540.0,
      "text": "We are underwater, nothing can get to us."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 85540.0,
      "end_time": 88470.0,
      "text": "No pests, means no chemicals needed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 88470.0,
      "end_time": 91720.0,
      "text": "and, of course, no hail, no storms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 91720.0,
      "end_time": 94250.0,
      "text": "the temperature stability that we have inside the water,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 94250.0,
      "end_time": 96170.0,
      "text": "which is a lot more stable than outside."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 96170.0,
      "end_time": 100100.0,
      "text": "Plus the higher pressure underwater, apparently,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 100100.0,
      "end_time": 102589.0,
      "text": "makes our plants grow faster and stronger"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 102590.0,
      "end_time": 105653.0,
      "text": "and with higher contents of essential oils."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 107420.0,
      "end_time": 109230.0,
      "text": "The water that we use for the plants"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 109230.0,
      "end_time": 113630.0,
      "text": "is mostly from evaporation of the surface of the saltwater."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 113630.0,
      "end_time": 117580.0,
      "text": "Once it's evaporated it condenses back into rain."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 117580.0,
      "end_time": 120710.0,
      "text": "We basically create freshwater automatically"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 120710.0,
      "end_time": 123113.0,
      "text": "that we don't need to consume any energy for."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 126519.0,
      "end_time": 128340.0,
      "text": "(soft piano music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 128340.0,
      "end_time": 131770.0,
      "text": "We know that climate change and the future of demography"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 131770.0,
      "end_time": 134340.0,
      "text": "is headed towards a way where we will be"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 134340.0,
      "end_time": 136820.0,
      "text": "overusing the resources of our planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 136820.0,
      "end_time": 139600.0,
      "text": "I hope that Nemo's Garden is a way to use those"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 139600.0,
      "end_time": 142973.0,
      "text": "resources in a very respectful way and balanced way."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 144160.0,
      "end_time": 146799.0,
      "text": "The whole concept for the project is to expand"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 146800.0,
      "end_time": 150350.0,
      "text": "the possibilities of agriculture."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 150350.0,
      "end_time": 153870.0,
      "text": "In a world that is covered more than 70 percent in water"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 153870.0,
      "end_time": 155373.0,
      "text": "it simply made sense to us."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 164633.0,
      "end_time": 167550.0,
      "text": "(electronic music)"
    }
  ]
